      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "When requesting time off in the CloudFlow portal, begin by accessing the \"Leave Request\" tab in your calendar section, then click \"Submit a Request.\" Next, email [YourTeamLead@CloudFlow.com](mailto:YourTeamLead@CloudFlow.com), including a brief explanation of your leave dates. \n\nPlease provide at least two weeks' notice, but no more than six weeks' for a standard request. Remember to include necessary details such as flight arrangements, work coverage, and any crucial deadlines. Once approved, you can finalize details through the portal, selecting your requested leave dates from the calendar grid and clicking \"Apply.\"",
      "source": "target",
